article_node.title: Innovative Solutions Announces Successful Use of DarcyIQ in Strategic Collaboration Agreement with AWS Focused on Smaller Businesses
article_node.summary: Innovative Solutions, a Premier Tier AWS Partner, announced key milestones in its Strategic Collaboration Agreement with AWS aimed at helping SMBs grow on the cloud. The company leveraged its DarcyIQ agentic AI platform to triple SMB customer acquisition in eight months and expanded its Boca Raton headquarters to support the partnership. AWS co‑invested in go‑to‑market activities and SMB support initiatives, while Innovative added new products and built technology that lets businesses purchase AWS services without building from scratch. With competencies in Generative AI, migrations, DevOps, and networking, Innovative offers managed services, cloud migrations, and AI solutions tailored to manufacturing, retail, finance, and life sciences. The firm emphasizes a customer‑first approach, boasting 99.7% client retention and a team of over 100 cloud‑certified professionals.
